libutf8 (1.0.0-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * Initial release.
  * Permissive UTF-8 encode/decode for unsigned 32-bit values.
  * Supports 1-6 byte sequences (up to 31 bits).
  * Returns 0 from utf8enclen for unencodable values (>0x7FFFFFFF).

